#. type: Title ==
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:205
#, no-wrap
msgid "Fluid Transport"
msgstr "流体运输"

#. type: #fluid
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:208
msgid ""
"When you have a compatible fluid transportation mod installed, factory "
"gauges placed in factory controllers may utilize that mod's ability to "
"transport fluids, and use fluids as ingredients or outputs."
msgstr ""
"安装兼容的流体物流模组后，控制台内的工厂仪表可以使用该模组的流体运输能力，将"
"流体作为原材料或产物。"

#. type: Block title
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:209
#, no-wrap
msgid "Compatibility of fluid transportation mods"
msgstr "流体物流模组的兼容性"

#. type: Table
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:212
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mod"
msgstr "模组"

#. type: Table
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:214
#, no-wrap
msgid "Compatibility"
msgstr "兼容性"

#. type: Table
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:215
#, no-wrap
msgid "Create: FluidLogistic"
msgstr "流体包裹（Create: FluidLogistic）"

#. type: Table
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:217 ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:223
#, no-wrap
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

#. type: Table
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:218
#, no-wrap
msgid "Create: Fluid"
msgstr "流体（Create: Fluid）"

#. type: Table
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:220
#, no-wrap
msgid "Yes, but may drop support in the future"
msgstr "是，但未来可能停止维护兼容性"

#. type: Table
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:224
#, no-wrap
msgid "Create Factory Logistics"
msgstr "Create Factory Logistics"

#. type: Table
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:225
#, no-wrap
msgid "No, will crash the game"
msgstr "不，会导致游戏崩溃"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:228
msgid ""
"When using Create: Repackaged, place fluid gauges provided by this mod to "
"monitor and produce fluids. Fluids may be set in the <<figure-set-item,\"set "
"item\" screen>> by clicking the filter slot while holding a bucket of fluid "
"or by dragging a fluid entry from JEI."
msgstr ""
"使用 Create: Repackaged 时，需要放置该模组提供的流体仪表来监测和生产流体。"
"在<<figure-set-item,“设置物品”界面>>中，手持装有目标流体的桶并点击过滤槽，或"
"直接从 JEI 拖入流体条目。"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:230
msgid ""
"When using the other mods, regular factory gauges gain the ability to "
"monitor and produce fluids. Fluids may be set in the <<figure-set-item,\"set "
"item\" screen>> by right-clicking the filter slot while holding a bucket of "
"fluid or by dragging a fluid entry from JEI."
msgstr ""
"使用其他兼容模组时，普通工厂仪表会获得监测和生产流体的能力。在<<figure-set-"
"item,“设置物品”界面>>中，手持装有目标流体的容器（例如桶）并右键点击过滤槽，或"
"从 JEI 拖入流体条目。"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:232
msgid ""
"Fluids do not contain NBT data, therefore when monitoring a fluid, the "
"option to ignore NBT data disappears."
msgstr "流体不包含 NBT 数据，因此在监测流体时，“忽略 NBT”选项会消失。"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:234
msgid ""
"When using a fluid as an ingredient or output, scrolling on the ingredient "
"or output UI adjusts the amount by 1 B. Hold shift while scrolling to adjust "
"by 10 mB, or hold ctrl while scrolling to adjust by 1 mB. The output is "
"limited to 10 B per batch."
msgstr ""
"将流体作为原材料或产物时，在对应槽位上滚动默认以 1 B 为单位调整，按住 Shift "
"滚动以 10 mB 为单位调整，按住 Ctrl 滚动以 1 mB 为单位调整。每批产物流体最多"
"为 10 B。"

#. type: Title ==
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:236
#, no-wrap
msgid "Promise Limits"
msgstr "承诺与待处理请求限制"

#. type: #promise
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:239
msgid ""
"Each time a factory gauge requests a set of ingredients to be sent to its "
"destination address, a promise is created (also referred to as a pending "
"request). Each promise records the number of expected to be produced, but "
"have yet to arrive in storage. When accounting for the number of monitored "
"items in storage, the number of items recorded in promises is added to the "
"actual storage amount before being compared to the target amount. Doing so "
"stops the factory gauge from excessively sending ingredients before the "
"outputs of previous requests arrive."
msgstr ""
"工厂仪表每次请求把一批原材料发往目标地址时，都会创建一项“承诺”，也称为待处理"
"请求。每项承诺会记录预计生产但尚未进入库存的产物数量。仪表在比较库存和目标数"
"量时，会先把承诺中记录的数量加到实际库存中。这样可以避免上一批产物尚未返回时"
"，仪表继续过量发送原材料。"

#. type: Block title
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:240
#, no-wrap
msgid "UI elements related to promises"
msgstr "承诺相关的界面元素"

#. type: #promise
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:245
msgid ""
"❶ Promised items:: Displays the total number of items recorded in promises "
"created by all gauges in the same network producing the same item. Click to "
"void all promises of the same item type."
msgstr ""
"❶ 承诺物品数量:: 显示同一网络内所有生产相同物品的仪表所创建的承诺中的物品数量"
"总和。点击以作废全部承诺。"

#. type: #promise
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:249
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"❷ Expire time::\n"
"Scroll to set the time interval for a promise to expire after its creation. Can be 1 to 30 minutes. Promises never expire by default. +\n"
"  This option is useful when the ingredients do not reliably produce the expected output, such as with recipes with probabilities.\n"
msgstr ""
"❷ 过期时间:: \n"
"滚动可设置承诺创建后多久过期，可选 1 至 30 分钟，默认永不过期。 +\n"
"当配方不能稳定地产生预期产物，例如带概率的加工配方时，此设置很有用。\n"

#. type: #promise
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:253
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"❸ Pending requests::\n"
"Displays the number of pending requests created by this gauge image:symbol-gauge.png[,18,16]. Click to switch to displaying pending requests sent to the same address image:symbol-address.png[,18,16]. In either state, scroll to set a limit on the displayed number. When the limit is reached, the gauge pauses sending new requests. +\n"
"  Limiting pending requests is useful for preventing excessive packages from overloading transportation lines.\n"
msgstr ""
"❸ 待处理请求::\n"
"可显示由当前仪表创建的待处理请求数量 image:symbol-gauge.png[,18,16] ，点击以"
"切换为显示发送到同一地址的待处理请求数量 image:symbol-address.png[,18,16] 。"
"在任一状态下，滚动可设置数量上限。达到上限后，仪表会暂停发送新请求。 +\n"
"限制待处理请求可防止过多包裹使运输系统过载。\n"

#. type: Title ==
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:255
#, no-wrap
msgid "Redstone"
msgstr "红石"

#. type: #redstone
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:258
msgid ""
"A factory gauge can be connected to some other components, such as "
"xref:electron-tube.adoc[logical tubes] and xref:redstone-link.adoc[redstone "
"links], via redstone connections. When connected as the source, it outputs a "
"redstone signal when the amount of the monitored item in storage is equal to "
"or greater than the target amount. When connected as the sink, the factory "
"gauge is disabled when it is powered by redstone."
msgstr ""
"工厂仪表可通过红石连接与xref:electron-tube.adoc[逻辑管]、xref:redstone-"
"link.adoc[无线红石信号终端]等组件连接。作为红石连接的源头端时，当监测物品的库"
"存数量大于或等于目标数量，工厂仪表会输出红石信号。作为红石连接的目标端时，工"
"厂仪表收到红石信号后会暂停工作。"

#. type: Block title
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:259
#, no-wrap
msgid "A factory gauge disabled by an incoming redstone signal, and outputting a redstone signal"
msgstr "因输入红石信号而暂停、同时又输出红石信号的仪表"

#. type: #redstone
#: ../src/factory-gauge.adoc:262
msgid ""
"Additionally, when a factory controller block is redstone-powered, all "
"factory gauges inside are disabled."
msgstr "此外，工厂控制台方块本身被红石充能时，内部的所有工厂仪表都会暂停工作。"
